Description.value: This iFLow enables SAP SuccessFactors to receive notifications of completed assessments from ADP Tax Credits.

name.value: ADP Tax Credits SuccessFactors Connector Assessment Status Update

query.value: SELECT id FROM AssessmentOrder WHERE vendorCode = 'ADP' AND candidateId= ${property.CandidateId}

fields.value: orderId, status, statusDate, field1Key, field1Value, field2Key, field2Value, field3Key, field3Value, field4Key, field4Value, field5Key, field5Value, field6Key, field6Value, field7Key, field7Value, field8Key, field8Value, field9Key, field9Value, field10Key, field10Value, field11Key, field11Value, field12Key, field12Value, field13Key, field13Value, field14Key, field14Value, field15Key, field15Value, field16Key, field16Value, field17Key, field17Value, field18Key, field18Value, field19Key, field19Value, field20Key, field20Value,  statusDetails

wrapContent.value:
<exception>
	<integrationPackage>SAP SuccessFactors Integration with ADP Tax Credits</integrationPackage>
	<integrationFlow>ADP Tax Credits SuccessFactors Connector Assessment Status Update</integrationFlow>
	<integrationMessageId>${property.SAP_MessageProcessingLogID}</integrationMessageId>
	<date>${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss.SSSaZ}</date>
	<candidateId>${property.CandidateId}</candidateId>
	<assessmentOrderId>${property.CurrentAssessmentOrderId}</assessmentOrderId>
	<errorCode>${property.ErrorCode}</errorCode>
	<errorMessage>${property.ErrorMessage}</errorMessage>
	<exception>${exception}</exception>
	<messageHistory>${property.CamelMessageHistory}</messageHistory>
</exception>
